summary: Tweaked settings for the FXAA injector and ENB to give much more natural visuals to skyrim
descriptionHtml:
Tweaked settings for the FXAA injector and ENB to give much more natural visuals to skyrim

I did not create  or own ENB or the FXAA/post process Injector, I\'ve merely included the files for easy install
Just drop all the files into your skyrim folder, and over-write if necessary
If it crashes on start-up, try running the game in administrator mode or disabling the steam overlay.
author: Inzal
